OL,5, A jury has found a former civilian     
OL,6, member of Canada's national police     
OL,7, force guilty of leaking intelligence to
OL,8, suspected criminals.                   
OL,10,FCameron Ortis, 51, shared government   
OL,11,Fsecrets with organised crime figures,  
OL,12,Fthe eight-week trial in Ontario heard. 
OL,14,FOrtis had denied all charges against   
OL,15,Fhim, claiming he was working secretly  
OL,16,Fto prevent "a grave threat to Canada". 
OL,18,FThe case was the first time that       
OL,19,FCanada's current espionage law had been
OL,20,Ftested at trial.                       
